                             Subject : LANDUNITS

  Land-units *!  How to use land units
 Maintenance     The cost to maintain ships, planes, and land units.
    Mobility     How much mobility stuff costs
    Railroad     How railroads work
       Spies     How spies work
  Unit-types *   Description of the different types of land units

        army     Designate members of an "army"
     assault *   Attack coastal sector from ship
      attack *   Sector vs. sector combat
       board *   Board enemy ship
       build *   Build ships, planes, land units, nuclear weapons or bridges
     fortify *   Fortify a land unit
        land *   Report status of land units
       lbmap *   Big map of all your worldly knowledge around a land unit
      lboard *   Board enemy land unit
      lcargo *   List the commodities on board your units
       ldump     Dump raw land unit information
       lload *   Load things onto land units
    llookout *   Check from units for other units, planes and/or sector types
        lmap *   Map around a land unit
       lmine     Mine a sector with an engineering unit
        lost *   Report lost items
      lradar     Use a radar unit's radar
    lretreat     Set retreat conditions/paths for units or armies
       lstat *   Report statistics of unit, army or units in a given area
       ltend     Transfer things between a unit and the ship carrying it
     lunload *   Unload things from land units
       march *   Move a land unit or units
     mission *   Assign a mission to a ship/plane/unit
      morale     Change the retreat percentage of a unit
    sabotage *   Damage enemy territory with spy unit
       scrap *   Scrap a ship, plane, or land unit
     scuttle *   Destroy a ship, plane, or unit
        show *   Characteristics of sectors, units, updates and more
       start     Resume production and repairs
        stop     Stop production and repairs
      supply *   Cause a unit to draw supplies
     upgrade     Update the tech of a ship/unit/plane to the current tech lev-
                 el
        work     Use engineers to raise sector efficiency
       xdump     Extended dump of everything under the sun

For info on a particular topic, type "info <topic>" where <topic>  is  one  of
the topics listed above.  Topics marked by * are the most important and should
be read by new players.  Topics with unusually long info are marked with a !.

